  ##If you have British national (overseas) status

  You can apply for a [British National Overseas (BNO) visa](https://www.gov.uk/british-national-overseas-bno-visa) to live, work and study in the UK.

  With this visa you can:

  + work in the UK without a job offer
  + be an employee, self-employed or a director of a company

  ###Eligibility

  The eligibility criteria include:

  - currently living in Hong Kong as your permanent home, if you're applying outside the UK
  - being aged 18 or older

  ###How long you can stay

  You can apply to stay for either:

  + 2 years and 6 months
  + 5 years

  If you want to stay longer, you can apply to extend your visa as many times as you want. After 5 years, you may be able to apply to settle permanently in the UK.

